title: Miss Mend
actors: Natalya Glan, Igor Ilyinsky, Vladimir Fogel, Boris Barnet, Sergey Komarov, Ivan Koval-Samborsky, Natalya Rozenel, Mikhail Rozen-Sanin, Tatyana Mukhina, Pavel Poltoratskiy, Anel Sudakevich, Mikhail Zharov
description: Three reporters and an office girl are trying to stop a bacteriological strike by some powerful western business leaders against the USSR.

title: Norte, hangganan ng kasaysayan
actors: Sid Lucero, Archie Alemania, Angeli Bayani, Mailes Kanapi, Mae Paner, Soliman Cruz, Hazel Orencio, Ian Lomongo, Kristian Chua, Noel Sto. Domingo, Perry Dizon, Raymond Lee, Sheenly Gener, Dea Formacil, Kristine Kintana
description: An embittered law student commits a brutal double murder; a family man takes the fall and is forced into a harsh prison sentence; a mother and her two children wander the countryside looking for some kind of redemption.
